​Cube Takeover: Successfully channel a matching color stream into the opponent's Energy Cube, draining it to 0.
​The Burn Away: During "Sudden Death," outlast the opponent's connections. If an opponent's cards are disconnected from their Cube for more than 2 turns, they "Short Out" and are removed, leaving the Cube defenseless.
​Optical Critical: Aligning a perfect, un-interrupted color chain of 10+ cards creates a surge that pierces all Encryption, resulting in an instant win.
